data.description: Welcome to Rarity Bay, Gated, Private Country Club Golf & Lake community.  This OPEN CONCEPT home is on a dead end cul-de-sac with almost no traffic.  PEACE & QUIET.  Seasonal peak of the lake too.  Large deck + Large screen room to enjoy Tennessee outdoor living.  WHITE IVORY KITCHEN with natural gas cooking.   Formal dining room + Breakfast Room + Breakfast bar.  The Living room has coffered ceilings, a wonderful fireplace, built ins and a wall of windows.  The OVERSIZED MASTER SUITE has trey ceiling, crown molding, large master closet and a grand Master Bathroom.  The office has cherry built-ins.  Lower level: Bedroom #2 & #3, Full bathroom, Recreation room with wet bar & Oversized unfinished storage/workshop with a roll up door.  Impeccably clean and maintained.  Come live the dream!
